SOWETO - eNCA will host its final Town Hall Debate in Orlando East Communal Hall, Soweto on Thursday. eNCA's political editor Vuyo Mvoko and senior anchor Dan Moyane will put the ANC, the DA and the EFF front and centre for 90 minutes of hard-hitting debate. WATCH: eNCA Town Hall Debate - Mbombela As election day approaches, party leaders will go toe to toe on the big issues facing South Africa.